snippet.title: The Good In Amber Heard!?
snippet.description:
In this video I compare the good things that are being said about Johnny Depp to the good things being said about Amber Heard.  Now don't judge her to harshly, after all "no matter how flat a pancake is, it still has two sides." Maybe, just maybe there is some good in her. Stick around to the very end to hear what that "good" could possibly be. 

A big shoutout goes to Savvy? on Twitter who created the posts about Johnny and allowed me to share them here. Please visit her Twitter page to see more.
